query: Show me revenue by region and segment
sql:
SELECT
    SUM(m.won_amount) AS total_revenue, f.region, m.segment
FROM cisco_stage_app.metrics AS m
    INNER
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.linearity_metrics AS l
    ON m.segment = l.segment
    INNER
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.funnel_metrics AS f
    ON m.segment = f.segment
    LEFT
    JOIN cisco_stage_app.qtd_commit_upside AS q
    ON m.segment = q.segment
GROUP BY f.region, m.segment
sql_formatted:
